                        div(class="row"): div(class="col-flex-sm10 col-center")
                            h6 Now read the following sentences:

                            p(class="mt20")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  1.
                                | The burglar #[strong can’t have entered] the house through one of the windows. They are too small.

                            p(class="mt20")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  2.
                                |  If the burglar was alone, he #[strong can’t have taken ] many things with him.

                    div(class="col-flex-sm11 col-flex-md6 col-center")

                        div(class="row mt100-md mt30-xs")
                            ul(class="c-list" data-ejercicio="")
                                h6 Complete the following sentences using #[strong can’t have + past participle]:

                                p(class="mt30")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  1.
                                    |  The burglar
                                    strong (get)
                                    span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Write here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                    | in through the windows. They are too small.

                                p
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  2.
                                    |  If he was alone, he
                                    strong (taken)
                                    span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Write here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                    too too many things with him.
                                p
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  3.
                                    |  He
                                    strong (make)
                                    span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Write here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                    | too much noise, because the dogs didn’t bark.

                                p
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  4.
                                    |  If he was quick, he
                                    strong (search)
                                    span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Write here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                    | all the house.

                                p
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  5.
                                    |  He
                                    strong (find)
                                    span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Write here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                    | the safe box. It is very well hidden.








